overview.en: FIC is the aggregation token of the IPFS network. The two major landing ecosystems of FIC include KT80s++ mining machine and KLUUK browser. KT80s++ mining machine can directly mine FIL by staking FIC and KLUUK browser can participate in retrieval and storage by staking FIC to obtain rewards FIC.
overview.zh: FIC是IPFS网络的聚合Token，FIC的两大落地生态，包括KT80s++矿机和KLUUK浏览器，KT80s++矿机通过质押FIC可以直接挖FIL和KLUUK浏览器通过质押FIC参与检索、存储获得打赏奖励FIC。
